    <item>
      <title>Authorized keys on Windows</title>
      <link>/posts/system/development/auth-keys-on-windows/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>i70170@hotmail.com (Mike Chang)</author>
      <guid>/posts/system/development/auth-keys-on-windows/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Windows 匯入認證密鑰以建立 ssh 連線&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;將 &lt;code&gt;~/.ssh/foo.pub&lt;/code&gt; 複製到 &lt;code&gt;C:/ProgramData/ssh/administrators_authorized_keys&lt;/code&gt; (假定使用 foo.pub)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#c6d0f5;background-color:#303446;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-powershell&#34; data-lang=&#34;powershell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$username&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;my-account&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$serve&lt;/span&gt;-name = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;my-server&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$authorizedKey&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#99d1db&#34;&gt;Get-Content&lt;/span&gt; -Path &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$env:USERPROFILE&lt;/span&gt;\.ssh\foo.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ef9f76&#34;&gt;pub&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$remotePowershell&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;powershell Add-Content -Force -Path &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$env:ProgramData&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;\ssh\administrators_authorized_keys -Value &amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$authorizedKey&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;;icacls.exe &amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$env:ProgramData&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6d189&#34;&gt;\ssh\administrators_authorized_keys&amp;#34;&amp;#34; /inheritance:r /grant &amp;#34;&amp;#34;Administrators:F&amp;#34;&amp;#34; /grant &amp;#34;&amp;#34;SYSTEM:F&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#737994;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# Connect to the server and run the PowerShell command by using the $remotePowerShell variable.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; ssh &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$username&lt;/span&gt;@&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$serve&lt;/span&gt;-name &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f2d5cf&#34;&gt;$remotePowershell&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
